    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "Director of Special Investigations",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "\"Inter Continental",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "Aerial Research",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "Foundation",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "\"NOTICE!",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "\"To All Concerned:",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "\"If anyone has seen any unidentified flying objects--",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "known also as flying saucers--or knows anyone who has",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "seen them since January 1st, 1957, please contact us",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "immediately, giving full names and addresses of the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "witnesses to these sightings.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "\"We are in the process of setting up UFO observer Posts",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "all over the United States, Canada, Europe, Alaska,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "Australia, Japan, England, Africa, and South America.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "And each state, province or region will have its own",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "filter center which will serve as a receiving station",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "for all UFO reports and other associated data, a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "distribution point for material from headquarters, and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "as a general secretary for ICARF.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "\"Our filter-observer network is expanding by leaps and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "bounds, but we are still far from our goal.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "\"The Air Force investigation has either gone underground,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "or else they have the answer and are hiding the fact",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "from the public. The fact remains that millions of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "people continue to see these UFOs and the public still",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "doesn't know what they are.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "\"It is our purpose in organizing ICARF to find the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "answer to the UFO mystery, and give the facts to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "the public. And in order to do this we will need",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "the assistance of every person concerned. Persons",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "with movie and still cameras are particularly needed,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "for the emphasis is on photographic data, despite",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "the fact that sightings with binoculars and telescopes,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "sound detector and ham radio stations are also very",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "important in the process of our research.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
